metadata.name: Dreamcatcher Forest #261
metadata.description:
"Dreamcatcher Forest" is part of the fxhash interactive minting experience at Art Basel, Basel 2022. The illustration in this work draws inspiration from Native American dreamcatchers, a protective talisman crafted from beautifully intricate patterns of woven thread, built from natural materials & colorful beads.

Dreamcatchers are used to protect dreamers while they sleep. Good dreams are able to slip through the web to meet the sleeper beneath, while bad dreams are trapped and prevented.

- Use the "S" key to save a PNG image.
- Use the "P" key to export a print-quality image.

metadata.name: SWTBD - construction drawing #80
metadata.description:
Construction drawing of the "Several ways to break down" generative geometry system by Frederik Vanhoutte, @wblut

mouse:

click: toggle active mode. In active mode, a new iteration with the same starting geometry and identical features is generated every 10s.

keyboard:

'a' or 'A' : add a slice or point
'e': decrease explosion factor
'E': increase explosion factor
'r' or 'R': create a new iteration with the same starting geometry and identical features
'+' and '-': zoom in and out
arrow keys: rotate around and translate along the vertical axis

metadata.name: ylb-mess-A #354
metadata.description:
With colors and shapes reminiscent of childhood LEGO explorations, 'ylb-mess-A' explores the assembly process in reverse, using recursive subdivision to create detailed structures instead of progressively building a complex structure brick by brick. Although the tools I use to explore and create have changed over the years, this piece reminds me of the natural creative curiosity that was instilled in me at an early age, for which I am incredibly grateful.

metadata.name: Flow #467
metadata.description:
Flow is a collection of eye pleasing formula's in the form of patterns and colors.

Features include:
- Patterns
- Palettes
- Focus points
- Margins
- Sizes
- Spacings
- Color distribution patterns
- Modifiers
- Gradients
- Dots
- Overflow

Due to the large amount of calculations it may take a few seconds to generate.
The spinning indicator on the top right disappears when it is finished, this is the best moment to save.

Press [s] to save a high resolution PNG @ 9933x14043 pixels (A0 paper dimensions @ 300 DPI).

Flow By @OneDayOfCrypto, 2022
